{"tid":2310761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局向中小學發函 列「守法」、「同理心」為首要培育價值觀","createTime":"2020-12-03T13:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T14:24:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b89e44e97098652b21212f973a97dfefc18ce2a","tid":2310761,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄上月表示，將全面加強培育老師及學生的「守法」 和「同理心」。事隔一周，教育局今日（3日）向全港中小學發出通函，公布加入「守法」和「同理心」作為首要培育學生的正面價值觀和態度，以加強學校推行價值觀教育的工作。教育局期望，香港下一代品行端正，能具備廣闊的知識基礎，展現明辨慎思、道德判斷、善於溝通等能力，並對社會有承擔、具國家觀念、香港情懷和國際視野。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%99%BC%E5%87%BD-%E5%88%97-%E5%AE%88%E6%B3%95-%E5%90%8C%E7%90%86%E5%BF%83-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%96%E8%A6%81%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2587%25BD-%25E5%2588%2597-%25E5%25AE%2588%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%259F%25B9%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2580%25BC%25E8%25A7%2580%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPQ2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=b0d81a63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2587%25BD-%25E5%2588%2597-%25E5%25AE%2588%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%259F%25B9%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2580%25BC%25E8%25A7%2580%2F&h=29a3de10\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%99%BC%E5%87%BD-%E5%88%97-%E5%AE%88%E6%B3%95-%E5%90%8C%E7%90%86%E5%BF%83-%E7%82%BA%E9%